This was news to me, but
I was trying to play it cool.

43
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:11,330
So I asked him to remind me of
the title and then he told me.

44
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:16,400
The course was called CS373 How
to Program a Robotic Car.

45
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,800
And I was terrified.

46
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:22,080
I didn't know anything about
programming or robotics.

47
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:26,850
And I might have quit right then,
if I hadn't remembered that lesson.

48
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:30,830
And because I really believe
that anyone can learn anything,

49
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:33,400
I started learning and
I haven't stopped.

50
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,410
And now, here I am today.

51
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:39,730
